WEBVTT

00:12:29.750 --> 00:12:32.194
vođeni vlastitom željom,

00:12:32.194 --> 00:12:35.790
sposobni i spremni da tamo uspiju.

00:12:37.450 --> 00:12:39.800
Moram vam nešto priznati.

00:12:39.800 --> 00:12:43.000
Imam dvoje djece, Sawyera i Avery.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:44.736
Tinejdžeri su.

00:12:44.740 --> 00:12:46.824
I nekad davno,

00:12:46.824 --> 00:12:49.066
mislim da sam ih tretirala

00:12:49.066 --> 00:12:51.276
kao mala bonsai drvca.

00:12:51.276 --> 00:12:53.270
(Smijeh)

00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:56.364
Samo ću ih pažljivo sjeckati, podrezivati

00:12:56.364 --> 00:13:00.180
i oblikovati u neki savršen ljudski oblik